@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "User Interface\n(UI)" as UI
box "Backend System (Sistema AIT)" #LightBlue
    participant "HTTP Request" as HttpRequest
    participant "Route" as Route
    participant "VesselController" as Controller
    participant "VesselDto" as Dto
    participant "VesselService" as ServiceImpl
    participant "Vessel" as DomainEntity
    participant "ImoNumber" as ImoVO
    participant "VesselTypeId" as TypeIdVO
    participant "VesselOperator" as OperatorVO
    participant "VesselRepository" as RepoImpl
end box

Officer -> UI : 1: create or update vessel data
activate UI

UI -> HttpRequest : 1.1: POST /api/vessel OR PUT /api/vessel/{imo} \n (VesselCreateDto / VesselDto)
activate HttpRequest
HttpRequest -> Route : 1.2: Match Route
activate Route
Route -> Controller : 1.3: Invoke CreateVessel / UpdateVessel
activate Controller

Controller -> Dto : 1.3.1: Map request body to DTO
activate Dto
Dto --> Controller : 1.3.2: DTO instance
deactivate Dto

Controller -> ServiceImpl : 1.4: CreateVesselAsync / UpdateVesselAsync (VesselDto)
activate ServiceImpl

alt Create Vessel
    ' ** Detalhe do fluxo de criação **
    ServiceImpl -> DomainEntity : 1.4.1: Vessel.Create(\n imo, name, typeId, operator)
    activate DomainEntity

    DomainEntity -> ImoVO : 1.4.1.1: new ImoNumber(imo)
    activate ImoVO
    ImoVO --> DomainEntity
    deactivate ImoVO

    DomainEntity -> TypeIdVO : 1.4.1.2: new VesselTypeId(typeId)
    activate TypeIdVO
    TypeIdVO --> DomainEntity
    deactivate TypeIdVO

    DomainEntity -> OperatorVO : 1.4.1.3: new VesselOperator(operator)
    activate OperatorVO
    OperatorVO --> DomainEntity
    deactivate OperatorVO

    DomainEntity --> ServiceImpl : 1.4.2: New Vessel entity created
    deactivate DomainEntity

    ServiceImpl -> RepoImpl : 1.5: AddAsync(Vessel entity)
    activate RepoImpl
    RepoImpl --> ServiceImpl : 1.6: Entity persisted
    deactivate RepoImpl
else Update Vessel
    ' ** Detalhe do fluxo de atualização **
    ServiceImpl -> RepoImpl : 1.4.1: GetByImoAsync(imo)
    activate RepoImpl
    RepoImpl --> ServiceImpl : 1.4.2: Existing Vessel entity
    deactivate RepoImpl

    ServiceImpl -> DomainEntity : 1.4.3: UpdateName(name)
    activate DomainEntity
    DomainEntity --> ServiceImpl : 1.4.4: Name updated
    deactivate DomainEntity

    ServiceImpl -> DomainEntity : 1.4.5: UpdateVesselType(typeId)
    activate DomainEntity
    DomainEntity --> ServiceImpl : 1.4.6: VesselType updated
    deactivate DomainEntity

    ServiceImpl -> DomainEntity : 1.4.7: UpdateOperator(operator)
    activate DomainEntity
    DomainEntity --> ServiceImpl : 1.4.8: Operator updated
    deactivate DomainEntity

    ServiceImpl -> RepoImpl : 1.5: UpdateAsync(Vessel entity)
    activate RepoImpl
    RepoImpl --> ServiceImpl : 1.6: Entity persisted
    deactivate RepoImpl
end

ServiceImpl --> Controller : 1.7: VesselDto (created/updated)
deactivate ServiceImpl

Controller --> HttpRequest : 1.8: HTTP 201 Created / 200 OK (VesselDto)
deactivate Controller
deactivate Route
deactivate HttpRequest

HttpRequest --> UI : 1.9: HTTP Response
deactivate UI

UI --> Officer : 1.10: Display confirmation / new data

@enduml